Usage: %(progname)s [OPTION]... [LMS_HOST] [LMS_PORT] [PLAYER_MAC]

     -p, --path=PATH        Sets the library path of LMS to PATH
     -d, --debug            Run in debug mode

Default: LMS_HOST: %(host)s
         LMS_PORT: %(port)s
